<paragraph id="8BCEFC30FFCD9676FF6B5DF1FBC388EE" blockId="11.[178,1085,451,502]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">
C o m m e n t: The known distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7187B3FFCD9676FDA65DF1FD3C88C0" authorityName="ZHENG" authorityYear="1992" box="[639,766,451,472]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Nazeris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="truncatus">
<emphasis id="B9052022FFCD9676FDA65DF1FD3C88C0" box="[639,766,451,472]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">N. truncatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confined to the Emei Shan, 
<collectingRegion id="49B532D2FFCD9676FF6B5DD2FEC488EE" box="[178,262,480,502]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
, from where it has been recorded repeatedly (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE081C1FFCD9676FD0D5DD2FCA888EE" author="ASSING V" box="[724,874,480,502]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" pagination="125 - 170" refId="ref8081" refString="ASSING V. (2013 b): On the Nazeris fauna of China II. New species and records from Zhejiang, Sichuan, and Yunnan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Bonn Zoological Bulletin 62 (2): 125 - 170." type="journal article" year="2013">ASSING 2013b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE081C1FFCD9676FCAD5DD2FC7688ED" author="ASSING V" box="[884,948,480,501]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" pagination="11 - 32" refId="ref8129" refString="ASSING V. (2014 a): A revision of Nazeris. IV. New species from China, Taiwan, and Thailand, and additional records (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 7: 11 - 32." type="journal article" year="2014">2014a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE081C1FFCD9676FC665DD2FC3488EE" author="ASSING V" box="[959,1014,480,502]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" pagination="371 - 377" refId="ref8220" refString="ASSING V. (2015): A revision of Nazeris VII. Three new species and additional records from Nepal and China (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Biodiversitat und Naturausstattung im Himalaya 5: 371 - 377." type="journal article" year="2015">2015</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
